         <div type="translation">
            <p>i.  In fear approach the gate of the <foreign xml:lang="la">bema</foreign>.</p>
            <p>ii. Jesus Christ is victorious,</p>
            <p>iii. Lord, help your servant Philippos, a sinner. Amen.</p>
            <p>iv. Victory of <gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="unknown"/>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>Text i. is in verse. See discussion at <ref type="eAla-text" n="VIII.12" target=".xml"/>.</p>
         </div>
